{"tid":2450141,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"ETF成份股同ETF個價有咩關係?","createTime":"2021-03-17T07:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T08:16:04.000Z","uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2815794ca4e614c408ae4cd84eb251e27f51578d","tid":2450141,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"假設呢隻ETF有兩隻股<br />\nT股80%<br />\n現股價50<br />\n<br />\nR股20%<br />\n現股價20<br />\n<br />\n咁ETF個價應該係 ($50*80%)+($20*20%) ?<br />\n我當公式無錯先啦 因為重點唔係想問上面呢樣<br />\n計算結果係呢隻ETF值44蚊<br />\n<br />\n但買賣ETF個價係隨住成交波動架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁成份股升趺<br />\n其實唔直接影響ETF既價格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係發行商會自己左手交右手貼近番價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"eadf840cc09f91acd7c6be628ad4fd33f322673e","tid":2450141,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"從來無寫包單話ETF個價一定等於跟住個價<br />\n如果隻ETF無咩人買，個價可以長期低啲"},{"pid":"7f77c74e55837936bc555cd882c4bbc2968a5997","tid":2450141,"uid":17275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"Market maker會維持個合理價<br />\n<br />\n太高/太低可以做arbitrage令個價接近返合理價"},{"pid":"3b2826c2e91349b3ac6bd07462f0ceda3dd0bec1","tid":2450141,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:42:50.000Z","msg":"所以咪有discount/premium"},{"pid":"9d84bda423997f6cdb91e9c66e741afdf20932c3","tid":2450141,"uid":158933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"仲有管理費"},{"pid":"77fe616ca1e6e3774c0943e178d30198b157aa40","tid":2450141,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"NAV 用黎做參考價。"},{"pid":"a347bcfe721e9b73f6781b0eb43a925c14d79a48","tid":2450141,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"咁以後直接搵被低估既ETF<img sr